a.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive thank\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it wasn't for him coming back, I would not have done that,' Wilde told Sky.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999065633718501, \"rank\": 7.141534396116254e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wilde\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He saved me a lot of energy on the bike.'\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde also said he was 'stoked' to see Yee win gold.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wilde\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"Yee win gold\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Just a great race overall.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'Just a great race\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I missed out on the end, but we recover now and try to get another medal,' Wilde said.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9435608918530778, \"rank\": 0.05922380060842124, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngra